            "text": "[{\"config\":{\"deviceId\":\"persistent\",\"sessionId\":\"persistent\",\"tabId\":\"tab\",\"serverCookies\":true},\"header\":{\"data\":{\"language_code\":\"id\",\"cpus\":4,\"touch\":false,\"browser_platform\":\"Windows\",\"is_w2m\":false},\"device_id\":\"a.c.mq85pe4m.619b2cb7-8b39-4b5c-bd77-2f146bf0ca77\",\"session_id\":\"1781103701045_a.c.mq85pe4m.619b2cb7-8b39-4b5c-bd77-2f146bf0ca77\",\"app\":\"picsart.com\",\"market\":\"web\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"version\":\"0\",\"v\":\"1.101.3\",\"debug\":false,\"tier_id\":\"pro\",\"app_language\":\"en\",\"segments\":[\"2o2w\",\"2pud\",\"54yx\",\"65az\",\"6c22\",\"6deg\",\"8ccr\",\"dnwu\",\"ebdk\",\"gzqa\",\"h028\",\"h813\",\"hah4\",\"hf56\",\"j5nz\",\"j5rq\",\"k8js\",\"kux6\",\"moyb\",\"n1el\",\"nwcu\",\"p6d5\",\"p8v1\",\"qicm\",\"qix7\",\"sb8u\",\"sc1j\",\"tpki\",\"uqqa\",\"w1nv\",\"xznx\",\"zrop\"],\"experiments\":[{\"variant\":\"original\",\"name\":\"gjht\",\"trackable\":1,\"settings\":[\"flow_pmt_type\"],\"defer\":1,\"actual\":true}],\"user_id\":518374468020101,\"device_last_tier_id\":\"pro\"},\"events\":[{\"id\":\"5e04ece6-7876-42ed-b570-1f76245d2189\",\"filterId\":\"custom_eventai_gen_item_load\",\"event_type\":\"ai_gen_item_load\",\"data\":{\"touchPoint\":\"com.picsart.ai-playground:/ai-playground\",\"source_sid\":\"a.c.mq85pe4y.c6c6f2c4-b6f7-4f0e-b164-ebc409fc887c\",\"result\":\"success\",\"result_type\":\"result\",\"processing_time\":231745,\"settings\":{\"model\":\"seedance-2.0\",\"format\":\"video\",\"input_type\":\"t2v\",\"aspect_ratio\":\"9:16\",\"resolution\":\"1080p\",\"generate_audio\":\"true\",\"duration\":\"15\",\"ref_image_urls\":[\"https://cdn-editing-temp.picsart.com/editing-temp/cb21d730-9eee-41ea-bc5b-999e87c124f2.jpg\"]},\"prompt\":\"Durasi 15 detik.\\n\\nStoryboard hanya sebagai referensi adegan.\\n\\nBuat video interview realistis di area outdoor modern. Produk harus identik 100% dengan foto: blouse wanita warna hitam berbahan Toyobo, model longgar, kancing depan, detail renda hitam di bagian bawah, tanpa perubahan warna, bentuk, desain, ukuran, atau detail apa pun.\\n\\nAdegan 1:\\nInterviewer wanita cantik memegang mic dan bertanya:\\n\\\"Kak, kok blousenya kelihatan elegan banget?\\\"\\n\\nAdegan 2:\\nPengguna memperlihatkan bagian bahan dan detail renda bawah blouse.\\nPengguna menjawab:\\n\\\"Bahannya Toyobo, adem, jatuh, dan nyaman dipakai seharian.\\\"\\n\\nAdegan 3:\\nClose up blouse saat dipakai.\\nPengguna berkata:\\n\\\"Modelnya longgar, nyaman, dan bikin penampilan lebih rapi.\\\"\\n\\nAdegan 4:\\nInterviewer dan pengguna tersenyum ke kamera.\\nInterviewer berkata:\\n\\\"Cocok buat kerja, kuliah, arisan, sampai acara formal.\\\"\\n\\nPengguna berkata:\\n\\\"Klik keranjang di bawah.\\\"\\n\\nKarakter manusia realistis, natural, ekspresi ramah, gerakan ringan, pencahayaan cerah, kualitas video tinggi.\\n\\nJangan tampilkan storyboard, collage, panel komik, sketsa, screenshot, thumbnail, split screen, picture in picture.\\n\\nJangan tampilkan teks apa pun di dalam video.\\nJangan tampilkan subtitle.\\nJangan tampilkan watermark.\\n\\nNEGATIVE:\\nBLUR, ENGLISH, DISTORSI, TEXT, SUBTITLE, WATERMARK.\",\"sid\":\"65641ec1-1937-4a57-80bc-a436f6ffddce\",\"miniapp_id\":\"com.picsart.ai-playground\",\"origin\":\"editor\",\"package_id\":\"com.picsart.ai-playground\",\"app_version\":\"2.8.14\",\"platform_version\":\"\",\"metadata\":{\"event_id_source\":\"sdk\"},\"url\":\"https://picsart.com/ai-playground?model=seedance-2.0&mode=video\",\"tab_id\":\"a.c.mq85pe4y.c6c6f2c4-b6f7-4f0e-b164-ebc409fc887c\",\"previous_url\":\"https://picsart.com/ai-playground?model=veo-3.1-fast&mode=video\",\"referrer\":\"https://picsart.com/id/create/\"},\"timestamp\":1781103963782,\"event_id\":\"a.c.mq87ba12.6c79d777-eb5e-43a3-a276-4261873657ff\"}],\"attributes\":[]}]"
          }
        },
